snippet.title: Truth Tables - Tautology and Contradiction
snippet.description: Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Truth Tables - Tautology and Contradiction.  In this video I construct two more truth tables and use them to illustrate the notion of a tautology and a contradiction.
